  <brief_title>Validation of a Questionnaire for Measuring Quality of Life in Patients With Chronic Inflammation of the Middle Ear</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of a Questionnaire for Measuring Health-related Quality of Life in Patients With Chronic Otitis Media</official_title>
